nder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇手機順便睇埋樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望住電話唔代表佢望唔到地下<br />\n如果有人望住個天行就真係望唔到地下啦<br />\n唔係的話唔多唔少都會望到地下"},{"pid":"a7d02542ef64883fa165b61f1b0b8f4d87bb3412","tid":456833,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:39:07.000Z","msg":"著四吋高鞋一定要望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時就都ok嘅"},{"pid":"f7753dbca66d2f0346462ee7a2d68a22cb2625f9","tid":456833,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T06:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔望地下點睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你冇見過人一路睇手機一路落樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇手機順便睇埋樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望住電話唔代表佢望唔到地下<br />\n如果有人望住個天行就真係望唔到地下啦<br />\n唔係的話唔多唔少都會望到地下</blockquote><br />\n但係我係一定要全程望住 <br />\n落樓梯個陣望前面唔望腳底行兩步都覺得會跌"}]}